<HEADLINE>
FT  05 AUG 93 / People: LMG William Thyne
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Ian Whitehead has been appointed md of LMG William Thyne on the retirement
of Bill Sinclair.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
